descriptionHTML:
Sleek WatchFace impresses with its Unique Design. Perfect for all shaped devices.

Match your smartwatch to your ensemble with this superbly stylish InAnT - designed watch face. A must for modern ladies and tech-savvy gents, where delightful detail is revealed with each passing moment.

Sleek WatchFace is a premium and thoroughly tested watch face application.
